All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<I18nReportableEnum>, Reportable
@Persistent
public class CompressionType
extends I18nReportableEnum

Enumerated type for GZip supported compression types (extra flags in GZip header).

Valid values are defined in a injected resource bundle but limited to the values listed in the GZip RFC: MAXIMUM_COMPRESSION and FASTEST_ALGORITHM. If no bundle is injected, all mapped value will be marked as not valid.
